docs.snippet: One man was killed and two women wounded when a gunman opened fire with an assault rifle at a house across the street from a polling station in the Southern California town of Azusa on Tuesday, police said, before the gunman was also found dead....
docs.lead_paragraph: One man was killed and two women wounded when a gunman opened fire with an assault rifle at a house across the street from a polling station in the Southern California town of Azusa on Tuesday, police said, before the gunman was also found dead.

headline.main: Two Dead, Two Wounded by Gunfire Near California Polling Place
headline.print_headline: Two Dead, Two Wounded by Gunfire Near California Polling Place
